Grammar

    0 $accept: Program $end

    1 Program: Decls

    2 Decls: Decls Decl
    3      | ε

    4 Decl: FuncDecl
    5     | VarDecl
    6     | TypeDecl

    7 FuncDecl: VarType IDENTIFIER LPARENTHESES ParamList RPARENTHESES SEMICOLON
    8         | VarType IDENTIFIER LPARENTHESES ParamList RPARENTHESES FuncBody

    9 FuncBody: LBRACE Stmts RBRACE

   10 VarDecl: VarType VarList SEMICOLON

   11 TypeDecl: _VarType SEMICOLON

   12 VarType: _VarType
   13        | CONST _VarType

   14 _VarType: BuiltinType
   15         | STRUCT IDENTIFIER LBRACE FieldDecls RBRACE
   16         | UNION IDENTIFIER LBRACE FieldDecls RBRACE
   17         | ENUM IDENTIFIER LBRACE EnumList RBRACE
   18         | _VarType ASTERISK
   19         | IDENTIFIER

   20 VarList: VarList COMMA VarInit
   21        | VarInit
   22        | ε

   23 VarInit: IDENTIFIER ArrayBoundList
   24        | IDENTIFIER ArrayBoundList ASSIGN Expr
   25        | IDENTIFIER ArrayBoundList ASSIGN LBRACE InitList RBRACE
   26        | IDENTIFIER ArrayBoundList ASSIGN LBRACE RBRACE

   27 InitList: InitList COMMA Expr
   28         | Expr

   29 ArrayBoundList: ArrayBoundList ArrayBound
   30               | ArrayBound
   31               | ε

   32 ArrayBound: LBRACKET INTEGER RBRACKET
   33           | LBRACKET RBRACKET

   34 ParamList: ParamList COMMA Param
   35          | ParamList COMMA ELLIPSES
   36          | Param
   37          | ELLIPSES
   38          | ε

   39 Param: VarType IDENTIFIER
   40      | VarType

   41 BuiltinType: CHAR
   42            | SHORT
   43            | INT
   44            | LONG
   45            | UNSIGNED
   46            | UNSIGNED CHAR
   47            | UNSIGNED SHORT
   48            | UNSIGNED INT
   49            | UNSIGNED LONG
   50            | FLOAT
   51            | DOUBLE
   52            | BOOL
   53            | VOID

   54 FieldDecls: FieldDecls FieldDecl
   55           | ε

   56 FieldDecl: VarType MemberList SEMICOLON
   57          | SEMICOLON

   58 MemberList: MemberList COMMA IDENTIFIER
   59           | IDENTIFIER
   60           | ε

   61 EnumList: EnumList COMMA Enum
   62         | Enum
   63         | ε

   64 Enum: IDENTIFIER
   65     | IDENTIFIER ASSIGN INTEGER

   66 Stmts: Stmts Stmt
   67      | ε

   68 Stmt: Expr SEMICOLON
   69     | IfStmt
   70     | SwitchStmt
   71     | ForStmt
   72     | DoStmt
   73     | WhileStmt
   74     | ContinueStmt
   75     | BreakStmt
   76     | ReturnStmt
   77     | Block
   78     | TypeDecl
   79     | VarDecl
   80     | SEMICOLON

   81 IfStmt: IF LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt ELSE Stmt
   82       | IF LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt

   83 SwitchStmt: SWITCH LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES LBRACE CaseStmtList RBRACE

   84 CaseStmtList: CaseStmtList CaseStmt
   85             | ε

   86 CaseStmt: CASE Expr COLON Stmts
   87         | DEFAULT COLON Stmts

   88 ForStmt: FOR LPARENTHESES Expr SEMICOLON Expr SEMICOLON Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt
   89        | FOR LPARENTHESES SEMICOLON Expr SEMICOLON Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt
   90        | FOR LPARENTHESES VarDecl Expr SEMICOLON Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt

   91 DoStmt: DO Stmt WHILE LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES SEMICOLON

   92 WhileStmt: WHILE LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt

   93 ContinueStmt: CONTINUE SEMICOLON

   94 BreakStmt: BREAK SEMICOLON

   95 ReturnStmt: RETURN SEMICOLON
   96           | RETURN Expr SEMICOLON

   97 Block: LBRACE Stmts RBRACE

   98 Expr: IDENTIFIER
   99     | Constant
  100     | LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES
  101     | Expr COMMA Expr
  102     | IDENTIFIER LPARENTHESES ExprList RPARENTHESES
  103     | Expr DOT IDENTIFIER
  104     | Expr ARROW IDENTIFIER
  105     | Expr LBRACKET Expr RBRACKET
